originalText.text: Jerry is a seasoned professional who has deep experience in the NY real estate market.  I have used him for several transactions, and without a doubt he has saved me a significant amount of money, and helped me avoid risky deals.  He has also guided me through deal complexities in a way that gave me comfort on the soundness of a transaction.  I would highly recommend Jerry to anyone seeking a first-rate attorney.

originalText.text:
Jerry Feeney and his team are outstanding. Although I know Jerry does a lot of closings for high end real estate in Manhattan, I was fortunate to learn that he also did closings outside of New York City and I chose him without hesitation to represent me and to assist with my closing on Greenwood Lake, NY.

He has a full team of skilled employees that very great in communicating to me and ensuring that I was informed throughout the entire process.  Jerry and his team were very methodical and seasoned in real estate transactions so it made the entire experience seamless, which is not always the case with real estate closings.

One thing to note is that Jerry was always available.  He was on a trip overseas and would be working on my closing and did conference calls with me even when he was out of the country.

I highly recommend The Law Offices of Jerry Feeney for your real estate transactions with no reservations.

originalText.text: Jerry and his staff are absolutely amazing! My husband and I worked with Jerry to buy a home in Greenwood lake NY and to say that the sellers were difficult would be putting it lightly. Jerry handled the transaction with all of the skill and charm that you would expect from someone with as distinguished a background as he. We are so happy to have found Jerry and plan to work with him on many more projects.

originalText.text: I was completely engaged during Jerry's class on legal pitfalls, law of agency and fair housing. His knowledge is encyclopedic, yet he conveys the information with energy and humor that held my attention for the day-long class. No one has ever explained the benefits of 1031 exchanges as well as Jerry does. And regarding the history of civil rights in the US, which is the basis of our fair housing laws, Jerry presented this information with detail and compassion. I would hire Jerry in a heartbeat as a closing attorney, because you get so much more for your money--his knowledge and abilities are so vast. I am so happy to know you, Jerry!

originalText.text: I attended Jerry’s seminar at REBNY on Legal Pitfalls faced in residential real estate in NY.  It also included fair housing and law of agency.  Jerry was fantastic!  He kept the class involved and enthusiastic about the topics using real life example and analogies to make sure we understood the subject matter being discussed.  He welcomed our questions about matters we have faced as residential salespeople and brokers.  This is not my first training with Jerry and certainly not my last.  He is very effective in getting the points across.
